{"tid":1434430,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"眼見和理非意向取代勇武 咁落去會輸","createTime":"2019-08-08T18:52:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T05:32:40.000Z","uid":38924,"like":63,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"301e1c5e16cbdeb99fbe5f3dcc4b7b4b03d4cc36","tid":1434430,"uid":38924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:52:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/wS0PDYcWh8U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FwS0PDYcWh8U&d=2tiv49EdsLtkS%2FsM0tMlCHXW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=a91546cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/wS0PDYcWh8U</a><br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以用少少時間睇條片<br />\n呢次係我第一次出post<br />\n希望大家唔好因為尖沙咀所擁有嘅自由 開心嘅感覺<br />\n而忘記我哋呢個盛夏承受嘅苦痛<br />\n民主仲有一段好長嘅路先可以達成<br />\n希望大家匆望初衷<br />\n咁落去和理非一旦取代勇武成為主流意見<br />\n我哋就輸啦 可以睇返14年雨革 大台充斥身邊<br />\n宜家今日所有熱門post已經出現返閑聊事 <br />\n已經忘記咗我哋呢兩個月嚟所有嘅辛酸<br />\n我想講 <strong>香港人並不善忘</strong><br />\n民主路充滿荊棘<br />\n但我哋攜手同行<br />\n香港人呢個身份終會成為我哋嘅驕傲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>光復香港 時代革命</strong>"},{"pid":"5442a2f2f915997f64e95fe07fde842e49467501","tid":1434430,"uid":38924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:52:37.000Z","msg":"自推10次 1/10"},{"pid":"9d146a4da28040649702b59477a4847a14200133","tid":1434430,"uid":38924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:52:51.000Z","msg":"自推10次 2/10"},{"pid":"1283eb5d15e1fde34c266651e5e983326a612bc3","tid":1434430,"uid":38924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:53:04.000Z","msg":"自推10次 3/10"},{"pid":"738638a8783b4987046f1d2c725ad93edd336d0c","tid":1434430,"uid":38924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:53:23.000Z","msg":"自推10次 4/10"},{"pid":"05039dd98ae35dda30419e4eba46700fd24411b8","tid":1434430,"uid":38924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:53:35.000Z","msg":"自推10次 5/10"},{"pid":"c96bb4f984f9dcdb1a6fb2dcd5f66358cf3a0201","tid":1434430,"uid":23385,"like":0,"dislike"