,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:54:37.000Z","msg":"自推10次 10/10"},{"pid":"020b50a006ecc9d6f2deff78b9768e549dde5024","tid":1434430,"uid":120729,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:54:50.000Z","msg":"熱門啲post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18a09fed9bb8f0944abbdbf065e47b24841d619f","tid":1434430,"uid":21920,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:55:50.000Z","msg":"輸字真難聽<br />\n你係裁判咩<br />\n輸輸輸<br />\n依家已經冇標籤啦<br />\n大家都係香港市民<br />\n從來唔分開兩派人"},{"pid":"a3df3186682e043d9baca45f78a9deab1c4be7ad","tid":1434430,"uid":38924,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ed7c7dff7747884b01e014498e70fdae19cfb338","tid":1434430,"uid":63117,"like":12,"dislike":3,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:54:25.000Z","msg":"幾時有講勇武退場<br />\n稍作休息唔得？？<br />\n連戰幾日勇武派唔攰？？？<br />\n講左雙管齊下和理非同勇武都缺一不可啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:55:55.000Z","msg":"宜家主流意見吹緊和理非 我唔理係咪3毛作祟<br />\n我只係想重提大家 匆忘初衷<br />\n和理非同勇武 缺一不可"},{"pid":"27517dc93b86cdec97132d447b68036d4eab6189","tid":1434430,"uid":41245,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:56:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">大家覺得加返deadline升級好唔好？</span><br />\n依家情況同上一個月差多<br />\n又係做好多嘢失去咗個目的同埋時限，搞到好似好迷失方向，和理非定勇武定包圍，行動上都係冇共識<br />\n加返deadline有好處<br />\n1.重申五大訴求，目標清晰，行動出師有名<br />\n2.訂立短中期行動計劃，例：今個禮拜和理非回合，唔回應就下個禮拜升級勇武行動<br />\n3.有計劃容易整合文宣<br />\n4.自己人有清晰目標，喺啲狗每日shift focus之下叫人專注返都易啲"},{"pid":"6db4a1d79a6cc68ec6adfe239d7c3a0b04e0d61f","tid":1434430,"uid":249296,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:56:08.000Z","msg":"相信大部份人都冇忘記過份苦痛<br />\n休息是為了走更遠的路<br />\n呢個標題好鬼<br />\n不推文"},{"pid":"9dbea1c04c1c638e79f077ad704fd9db194ebdd8","tid":1434430,"uid":251001,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:56:23.000Z","msg":"前線齊唱今天我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a213b2f2c9fd3c3f85226f6c0407a7021020ed8a","tid":1434430,"uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:56:40.000Z","msg":"一單還一單<br />\n你唔可以抽空context,現況<br />\n僅以理念嚟決定點做<br />\n<br />\n打麻雀咁<br />\n好咁就攻，閪牌就守博摸和<br />\n<br />\n你冇可能唔睇牌嚟諗攻定守"},{"pid":"3034b3e3e281c58f5bea49c41d38bb9498082da2","tid":1434430,"uid":38924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"18a09fed9bb8f0944abbdbf065e47b24841d619f","tid":1434430,"uid":21920,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:55:50.000Z","msg":"輸字真難聽<br />\n你係裁判咩<br />\n輸輸輸<br />\n依家已經冇標籤啦<br />\n大家都係香港市民<br />\n從來唔分開兩派人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:57:21.000Z","msg":"匆忘初衷 兩派這缺一不可<br />\n標題只想大家唔好比興奮充斥頭腦"},{"pid":"3ed9de5f54ffed9cfe9140e44f0bfdccf294ec17","tid":1434430,"uid":21920,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:58:17.000Z","msg":"興奮唔會長期<br />\n大家最終都會回到路上"},{"pid":"5f0e45785608e6ec06c5584c36c03df0a29deb35","tid":1434430,"uid":38924,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6db4a1d79a6cc68ec6adfe239d7c3a0b04e0d61f","tid":1434430,"uid":249296,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:56:08.000Z","msg":"相信大部份人都冇忘記過份苦痛<br />\n休息是為了走更遠的路<br />\n呢個標題好鬼<br />\n不推文"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:58:18.000Z","msg":"如果標題太鬼 我道歉<br />\n但你睇下熱門post 我好痛心"},{"pid":"2070cc70083e0ffc403a5a62422a1e3fb1cc0a93","tid":1434430,"uid":296222,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:58:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8789457db22c101772ef2a8b56a91f739e94f759","tid":1434430,"uid":38924,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:59:39.000Z","msg":"我重伸一次<br />\n兩派缺一不可<br />\n標題起得有問題我認錯<br />\n只為大家匆忘初衷<br />\n<br />\n利伸 中前線"},{"pid":"743e3975c4e3863442ad9b5f5a9a325b5a9d6cbe","tid":1434430,"uid":38924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T19:01:52.000Z","msg":"唔想惹起任何罵戰<br />\n<br />\nI love Hong Kong x 3000<br />\n<br />\n我好驕傲香港人身份！<br />\n<br />\n只為進諫同提醒大家<br />\n<br />\n<strong>匆忘初衷</strong><br />\n<br />\n同唔好忘記歷史教訓"},{"pid":"785ab180580cbf01c7ffcd4149d29d6d585e2c47","tid":1434430,"uid":235465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T19:05:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">和理非-&gt;死線-&gt;升級</span><br />\n明未"},{"pid":"3173702c76845d400776e81ad4b652bd474fff85","tid":1434430,"uid":38924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T19:06:16.000Z","msg":"自推<br />\n<br />\n不分化 不割蓆<br />\n<br />\n勇武決定一定撐"},{"pid":"096841543eefe404f511674b5d2a16285b3ba0eb","tid":1434430,"uid":206546,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T19:08:21.000Z","msg":"啱 set deadline 冇回應就勇武<br />\n和理非唔係接力勇武，係要一齊升級<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">兄弟爬山 各自修行</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"88483364616896c2d471aad7973d560e283b204e","tid":1434430,"uid":17060,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T19:08:30.000Z","msg":"該勇武時勇武，需要和理非時堅持和理非<br />\n大家運用自己嘅智慧<br />\n依家和理非對勇武比起14年已經包容左好多<br />\n好多落到場都已經唔會阻勇武，只係叫大家小心啲<br />\n我覺得已經係有進步<br />\n係等一個契機令和理非都勇武起來"},{"pid":"42dc9854001a83708c7be2924338e739d9d45d9e","tid":1434430,"uid":210140,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T19:08:43.000Z","msg":"我都係其他POST講到口乾<br />\n班人好鐘意用前線累/送頭/民意逆轉做包裝<br />\n唉"},{"pid":"92276f7ea33fa3bd759abbaffad0a446da12883b","tid":1434430,"uid":92188,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T19:09:46.000Z","msg":"勇武一定要繼續存在，但係點樣唔會變成鳩佔，而武力升級暫時已經到頂，好明顯和理非對火係好有保留，你都要比時間佢跟到勇武嘅步伐，暫時唔好挑戰佢哋對武力嘅接受程度"},{"pid":"5163ef61d0e37e6c0bf83cddb4354e79f4271fae","tid":1434430,"uid":161417,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"88483364616896c2d471aad7973d560e283b204e","tid":1434430,"uid":17060,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T19:08:30.000Z","msg":"該勇武時勇武，需要和理非時堅持和理非<br />\n大家運用自己嘅智慧<br />\n依家和理非對勇武比起14年已經包容左好多<br />\n好多落到場都已經唔會阻勇武，只係叫大家小心啲<br />\n我覺得已經係有進步<br />\n係等一個契機令和理非都勇武起來"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T19:10:19.000Z","msg":"係呀<br />\n和理非好多都進步咗<br />\n其他都快少少 勇武起來"},{"pid":"11e5bcd89a038b549100dd6c6327403e81645133","tid":1434430,"uid":161417,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"301e1c5e16cbdeb99fbe5f3dcc4b7b4b03d4cc36","tid":1434430,"uid":38924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:52:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/wS0PDYcWh8U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FwS0PDYcWh8U&d=2tiv49EdsLtkS%2FsM0tMlCHXW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=a91546cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/wS0PDYcWh8U</a><br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以用少少時間睇條片<br />\n呢次係我第一次出post<br />\n希望大家唔好因為尖沙咀所擁有嘅自由 開心嘅感覺<br />\n而忘記我哋呢個盛夏承受嘅苦痛<br />\n民主仲有一段好長嘅路先可以達成<br />\n希望大家匆望初衷<br />\n咁落去和理非一旦取代勇武成為主流意見<br />\n我哋就輸啦 可以睇返14年雨革 大台充斥身邊<br />\n宜家今日所有熱門post已經出現返閑聊事 <br />\n已經忘記咗我哋呢兩個月嚟所有嘅辛酸<br />\n我想講 <strong>香港人並不善忘</strong><br />\n民主路充滿荊棘<br />\n但我哋攜手同行<br />\n香港人呢個身份終會成為我哋嘅驕傲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>光復香港 時代革命</strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T19:11:19.000Z","msg":"條片好似我成個心聲咁<br />\n睇完深感認同"},{"pid":"8bcac7e41b34f70324c54d9ca38188d0f2a42fa1","tid":1434430,"uid":38924,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"42dc9854001a83708c7be2924338e739d9d45d9e","tid":1434430,"uid":210140,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T19:08:43.000Z","msg":"我都係其他POST講到口乾<br />\n班人好鐘意用前線累/送頭/民意逆轉做包裝<br />\n唉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T19:12:08.000Z","msg":"我明白！<br />\n<br />\n但機場和理非一定要支持<br />\n<br />\n同時間我只係有少少願望大家唔好因為一時嘅喜悅充斥頭腦<br />\n<br />\n勇武抗衡must go on<br />\n<br />\n只求和理非意見永不會好似雨革取代主流"},{"pid":"3ecf9920946e7b08eb1f22f31a4fa2cc3cb2d183","tid":1434430,"uid":161417,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T19:14:24.000Z","msg":"Do not Go Gentle into That Good Night<br />\n <br />\nDo not go gentle into that good night,<br />\nOld age should burn and rave at close of day;<br />\nRage, rage against the dying of the light.<br />\n <br />\nThough wise men at their end know dark is right,<br />\nBecause their words had forked no lightening they<br />\nDo not go gentle into that good night.<br />\n <br />\nGood men, the last wave by, crying how bright<br />\nTheir frail deeds might have danced in a green bay,<br />\nRage, rage against the dying of the light.<br />\n <br />\nWild men who caught and sang the sun in flight,<br />\nAnd learn, too late, they grieved it on its way.<br />\nDo not go gentle into that good night.<br />\n <br />\nGrave men, near death, who see with blinding sight<br />\nBlind eyes could blaze like meteors and be gay,<br />\nRage, rage against the dying of the light.<br />\n <br />\nAnd you, my father, there on the sad height,<br />\nCurse, bless me now with your fierce tears, I pray.<br />\nDo not go gentle into that good night.<br />\nRage, rage against the dying of the light."},{"pid":"92601417c2982261b634bd5865907be7c39c708e","tid":1434430,"uid":38924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T19:16:03.000Z","msg":"繼續自推<br />\n<br />\n和理非同勇武永成一線<br />\n<br />\n不割蓆 不篤灰<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人係我哋驕傲</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"03e0cd2abcf379be29b2836d025a1b5f18b29e70","tid":1434430,"uid":210140,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8bcac7e41b34f70324c54d9ca38188d0f2a42fa1","tid":1434430,"uid":38924,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"42dc9854001a83708c7be2924338e739d9d45d9e","tid":1434430,"uid":210140,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1